subject from srebrenica doctor in hell srebrenica s doctor recount town s live hell by laura pitter tuzla bosnia reuter neret mujanov wa a pathologist when he trek through the mountain to the besieg muslim town of srebrenica last august but after treat mangl victim of bosnia s bloodi war he consid himself a surgeon now i m a surgeon with great experi although i have no licens to practic but if i oper on a person and he live normal that s the greatest licens a surgeon could have evacu by the u n thi week to hi home town of tuzla the muslim physician gave an eyewit medic assess of the horror of the year long serb sieg of srebrenica and the suffer of the thousand trap there i live through hell togeth with the peopl of srebrenica all those who live through thi ar the greatest hero that human can produc he told report mujanov had practic for two month as an assist at a local hospit in tuzla but befor go to srebrenica he had never perform a surgic oper on hi own now he sai he ha perform major surgeri time reli on book for guidanc amput arm and leg time usual without anesthet deliv babi and perform four cesarean section he work to hour dai slept in the hospit for the first week after hi arriv last aug and treat patient he arriv after make the trek over mountain on foot from tuzla mile northwest of srebrenica about other peopl carri in suppli and soldier guid and protect him through guerrilla terrain he said hi worst memori wa of dai ago when seven serb shell land within on minut in an area half the size of a footbal field kill peopl immedi and wound half of the dead were women and children the peopl had come out for a rare dai of sunshin and the children were plai soccer there wa no warn the blood flow like a river in the street he said there were piec of women all around and you could not piec them togeth on woman hold her two children in her hand wa ly with them on the ground dead thei had no head befor mujanov arriv with hi suppli condit were deplor he said mani death could have been prevent had the hospit had surgic tool facil and medicin the six gener practition who had been oper befor he arriv had even less surgic experi than he did thei didn t know the basic principl for amput limb onc he arriv the situat improv he said but by mid septemb he had run out of suppli bandag were wash and boil five time sometim thei were fall apart in my hand he said doctor had no anesthet and could not give patient alcohol to numb the pain becaus it increas bleed peopl were complet consciou dure amput and stomach oper he said blood transfus were imposs becaus thei had no facil to test blood type i felt destroi psycholog mujanov said the situat improv after dec when a convoi arriv from the belgian medic group medecin san frontier but mujanov said the militari predica worsen in mid decemb after bosnian serb began a major offens in the region everi dai we had air strike and shell then the hunger set in between mid decemb and mid march when u s plane began air drop food between and peopl were dy everi dai from complic associ with malnutrit he said i know for sure that the air drop oper save the peopl from massiv death by hunger and starvat he said accord to mujanov around peopl di in srebrenica of them children dure a year of sieg mujanov plan to return to srebrenica in three week after visit hi wife who is ill in tuzla thei sai i m a hero he said there were thousand of peopl stand at the side of the road cry and wave when i left and i cri too sharon machli gartenberg framingham ma usa e mail sharon world std com 